title: Celebrities.Undercover.S01E01.Wendy.WilliamsAnd.Kim.Kardashian.W
description:
Description 
 Celebrities Undercover is a half hour celebrity driven comedic reality show full of candid, OMG moments where the viewer gets to see another, never-before-seen side of a celebrity. Each episode will follow two celebrities on a mission as they seek truth through anonymity, going undercover - amidst friends, fans and colleagues - in order to gain insight that is impossible to obtain without being disguised. Can they trick them while remaining incognito? Part "mission impossible" and part hidden camera social experiment, observe these pop-culture personalities outside of the comforts of their familiar element.

Episode 1
 Wendy Williams & Kim Kardashian
 Released Mar 19, 2014
 Talk show host Wendy Williams goes undercover as a member of her own audience and "Keeping Up With the Kardashians" reality star Kim Kardashian disguises herself at a group job interview as a fan hoping to become her new assistant.
